---
title: Mexican Red Kidney Bean & Veggie Filo Pie with Cucumber Salad & Coriander
description: When you fuse beans and pastry you get this amazing red kidney bean filo pastry pie. There’s veggies packed in and cooked
through a fiery tomato sauce to make a filling that will make your mouth water. It’s a perfect combination!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65b1c7cf553f74890680db94-b59dd1e3.jpeg
